      "raw_text": "Land owners near Pasco have\nclosed deal with Robert E. Stra-\nhorn of Spokane and P. A. Devers\nof Portland for the irrigation of at\nleast 5000 acres. The land pro-\nposed to be watered is large\nplain that contains some of the\nfinest agricultural land in the\nstate. Pasco is delighted over the\ndeal, as it gives promise of making\nthat place another Wenatchee. ="
